        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Master's in CS</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Advanced 2-year program focusing on research, AI, machine learning, and specialized computer science domains.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
