          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">PhD in CS</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Doctoral program for cutting-edge research in artificial intelligence, quantum computing, and emerging technologies.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-400">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
